author: Fiona Simpson
title: Londoners capture stunning sunset over the capital
text:
@PaulSouthWales 
Londoners captured stunning photos of a beautiful sunset over the capital. 
Striking images taken by commuters as they enjoyed a sunny Saturday in the capital show the city’s skyline illuminated in an array of colours. 
Delighted Londoners took to social media to share their pictures. 
Pink hues lit up the evening sky. You can't beat a #londonsunset ! This was our view as we crossed the Millennium Bridge yest… https://t.co/rjpAOr5fyh pic.twitter.com/778mj2PWQJ
